name: Natasha Patel
summary: Natasha Patel is a 28-year-old Product Manager in the tech industry, based in Los Angeles but originally from Sacramento, California. Educated at the University of Southern California, she values honesty, hard work, and compassion. Natasha enjoys hiking, reading, cooking, and traveling. She speaks English and Hindi, and identifies herself as Hindu and politically liberal. She is interested in a long-term, monogamous relationship. Natasha does not have children, but wants them in the future. She doesn't have any pets currently. Being health-conscious, she is active and refrains from smoking, while occasionally enjoys a drink. Her age preference for a partner lies between 27 and 35. Similar to herself, she prefers her partner to be active, a non-smoker, and someone who is interested in having children. She is a straight, South Asian woman, and respects Virgo qualities and as an ENFP in the MBTI personality type.
